---
---

<section id="about" class="section-py">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <p class="section-label reveal">
      <span class="lang-es">Sobre mí</span>
      <span class="lang-en">About</span>
    </p>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- ↓ FOTO — comentar este bloque para ocultar sin romper el layout -->
      <div class="photo-block reveal">
        <div class="photo-frame">
          <img
            src="/photo.jpg"
            alt="Juan Sebastián Sandoval"
            class="photo-img"
            loading="lazy"
            width="320"
            height="360"
          />
          <div class="photo-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- ↑ FIN bloque foto -->

      <!-- Text side -->
      <div class="text-side">
        <!-- Big number (decorative) -->
        <div class="years-block reveal">
          <span class="years-number">3+</span>
          <span class="years-label lang-es">años de<br />experiencia</span>
          <span class="years-label lang-en">years of<br />experience</span>
        </div>

        <p class="about-body reveal lang-es">
          Desarrollador Full Stack con más de 3 años construyendo aplicaciones
          web escalables. Trabajo con React, Node.js, PHP, TypeScript,
          PostgreSQL y MongoDB. Me interesa igual el rendimiento del sistema que
          la experiencia del usuario — el código limpio y las interfaces
          cuidadas no son opuestos.
        </p>
        <p class="about-body reveal lang-en">
          Full Stack Developer with over 3 years building scalable web
          applications. I work with React, Node.js, PHP, TypeScript, PostgreSQL,
          and MongoDB. I care equally about system performance and user
          experience — clean code and polished interfaces are not opposites.
        </p>

        <div class="location reveal">
          <svg
            width="14"
            height="14"
            viewBox="0 0 14 14"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.4"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <circle cx="7" cy="6" r="2.5"></circle>
            <path
              d="M7 1C4.5 1 2.5 3 2.5 5.5c0 3.5 4.5 7.5 4.5 7.5s4.5-4 4.5-7.5C11.5 3 9.5 1 7 1z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          San Gil, Santander, Colombia
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .section-label::after {
    content: "";
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* Grid collapses gracefully if photo block is commented out */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      /* auto handles the photo column — if photo removed, text takes full width */
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      gap: 5rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }

  /* Photo */
  .photo-block {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .photo-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 220px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .photo-frame {
      width: 240px;
    }
  }

  .photo-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top center;
    display: block;
    filter: grayscale(15%);
    transition: filter 0.4s;
  }

  .photo-img:hover {
    filter: grayscale(0%);
  }

  /* Decorative accent border offset */
  .photo-accent {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-accent);
    transform: translate(10px, 10px);
    z-index: -1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* Text side */
  .text-side {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }

  .years-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .years-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .years-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 400;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.15rem);
    line-height: 1.78;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .location {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
</style>
